3)insertBefore(): insert a new node before an existing node as child node of a specified parent
--requires a reference to both the new node and existing node  you want to insert before.

Ex:
<div id="a">
        <h1>ravi</h1>
        <h1 id="r">hari</h1>
    </div>
    <div id="b">
        <h2>ram</h2>
